The paper proposes a novel solution for location-based services in wireless networks using compressed sensing techniques. The paper involves signal processing, wireless communication, and distributed algorithms, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Systems and Control (cs.SY), Multiagent Systems (cs.MA), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
